Global Professional Liability Insurance Market Insights
Professional Liability Insurance Market size was valued at USD 50 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 85 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.3% from 2024 to 2030.

Professional Liability Insurance Market Overview
The global Professional Liability Insurance market has been experiencing significant growth over the years. The market was valued at approximately USD 80 billion in 2023 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 6.5% during the forecast period from 2024 to 2031. The increasing demand for legal protection against malpractice, negligence, and errors & omissions is a key factor driving this market. As businesses continue to face regulatory scrutiny, the adoption of professional liability insurance policies has become a critical tool for mitigating financial risks. The sector is poised for expansion as both small and large firms seek comprehensive risk management solutions.

